[Category "Partnership Bidding"]
[Difficulty "beginner"]
[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/basic_major"]
[Student "S"]
{WEST passes to start with since he only has 9 points.

EAST naturally opens 1\S with her 13 point, 5-card \S suit hand.

WEST might now make a Limit Raise since his hand is now worth 11 points because of the 
two doubletons. However, with six trumps he should jump all the way to 4\S.}

